Interface RpcServer.WorkerFactory

All Known Implementing Classes:
BasicWorkerFactory
Enclosing class:
RpcServer
public static interface RpcServer.WorkerFactory

Used by RpcServer to create RpcWorkers. A standard implementation is provided: BasicWorkerFactory. However, the user may create their own implementation if they desire more control over how Channels are allocated to RpcWorkers.
